```
INSERT INTO a SELECT * FROM system.one;
```
Takes 10 seconds as expected.

```
INSERT INTO a VALUES(1);
```
Takes 1 second, which is unexpected and means that the MVs are being executed in parallel even though `parallel_view_processing == 0`.

Fails for 21.11+
